The jQuery ClassyLoupe is a jQuery plugin that gives you the ability to add
zoom on hover ability for your photos with single line of code. With ClassyLoupe
you have the ability to control the zoom level and loupe size via mouse scroll
which gives you the opportunity to enlarge areas that you might be interested in.

@name ClassyLoupe
@package jQuery plugin
@author Marius Stanciu - Sergiu <marius@class.pm>
@website http://www.class.pm/
